  "summaries": [
    "The <b>Tungsten Bow</b> is a strong, mid-tier <linked>bow</linked> crafted solely using <linked>Tungsten Bars</linked>. It is stronger than its <linked>ore</linked> counterpart, the <linked>Silver Bow</linked>, and the ones that precede it in power. Like other bows, it uses arrows as ammo. It does not convert used arrows into special arrows.",
